PROJECT 6: Banking System (With Authentication + Transactions)
Features:
register/login system,deposit / withdrawal,transfer between accounts,transaction history,pin lockout after 3 wrong tries,persistent file database
Showcases:
structs,password hashing (simple),random account numbers,file database,edge-case handling

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PROJECT 7: Dynamic Data Structure Console App
Search:
by title,by author,by ID,
Sort:
alphabetical / ID,Borrow/return logic
Showcases:
linked lists,pointer manipulation,memory (malloc, free),struct relationships
